{"tid":2308582,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 香辣咸魚雞粒炒意粉","createTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T07:19:01.000Z","uid":33359,"like":89,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c9bb8ac2bf65eed4a5c7a612b41b1edef8b9c4a6","tid":2308582,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrVBrS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrVBrS4.jpg&h=f91e7a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZMhbjN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZMhbjN.jpg&h=3c5f6fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一聽到個菜名就覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開盒就聞到勁香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意粉炒得好乾身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然食唔到原塊咸魚肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但啖啖都有咸魚香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啲菇菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個口感同味道都好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最正仲有啲炸蒜酥係面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好惹味好香口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞粒比較遜色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乾同無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果換做啲爆炒過既雞絲會更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條阿基里斯腱好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開咗個講觀塘美食既mewe gp<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家已超過1300人入咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誠邀大家一齊入黎分享觀塘美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%B01&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=ef6f6261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1</a>"},{"pid":"aaa7fe66ba23a4942d85c73b8572f15214c0c3d5","tid":2308582,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fabedecc6923ec7e4f7472911f844eda22526d6","tid":2308582,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"開口師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4093c0acefc2748397262d2e4f1cf6af0cdf31a9","tid":2308582,"uid":129695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a8e6f2ece7b10ddb60e581fa9694a1adbcd48d","tid":2308582,"uid":157826,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"aaa7fe66ba23a4942d85c73b8572f15214c0c3d5","tid":2308582,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4787561d1e16914032aa1dfdfd4de62b3c5e63f5","tid":2308582,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"印仔冇wfh?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d756967d468189886b2d5d377f9c233780b1b492","tid":2308582,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"食屎仔<br />\n咁吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji